name: DD004 - Carmen Diablo
description:
DD004 - Carmen Diablo

Condition - Carmen Diablo has been split into 100 beings. This was an accidental fracturing. This is believed to have occurred on her 26th birthday, after graduating from corp training she entered the workforce experiencing immediate confusion and dissonance. As a result she reflexively split into 100 beings. Now Carmen has no idea who she is, some Carmens are angry, other prone to tearful combustion, Carmens 4,7 and 94 are lazy yet emit extreme heat. Carmen 4 once powered the city of Minneapolis from a hidden bunker facility under the airport. 

Dosage - Drug C8 (IV constant) 

Current action - Commit to private block on confirmed transaction.
